<h2 id="journey-so-far" style="text-align: center; margin-top: 40px;">Journey so far</h2>
<div style="display: flex; align-items: flex-start; margin: 20px auto; max-width: 80%;">
    <div class="journey-description" style="max-width: 100%; margin-right: auto; text-align: justify; color: gray; padding-left: 20px; font-size: 18px; margin-right: 0;">
        <p>I cherish moments spent with friends and family, and I’m actively involved in volunteering for community service. I’m proud to serve as the <strong>President of the Philippine Society of Youth Science Clubs (PSYSC)</strong>, where I get to lead initiatives that promote scientific awareness and environmental stewardship among my peers. I believe in the power of youth to create positive change, and I strive to inspire others to embrace science in their lives.</p>
        <p>I am also serving as the <strong>Sergeant at Arms for the Der Deutscherverein</strong> allows me to immerse myself in German culture while fostering connections with fellow students.</p>
        <p>Moreover, I am a <strong>photojournalist for The Vanguards</strong>, where I capture candid moments and tell stories through my lens.</p>
        <p>So, that’s me in a nutshell: a curious, chaotic, science-obsessed student who’s still figuring things out, but enjoying the ride along the way.</p>
    </div>
